channel.title: I got DoSed ant this happened..WHY?
channel.description: My server was running fine for the past 4 weeks, until i got in an argument with someone, and he decided to DdoS it. Then this happened everytime I run and try to play on my server. ANY HELP? I've tried to make a new webclient, redownload a new source. nothing fixed it, I tried clearing my cache. Nothing [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/qs62bb.png[/img]
